TESTIMONIAL_SECTION_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER: Don't just take our word for it - hear from developers using our Ethereum transaction monitoring app.
TESTIMONIAL_1_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Being able to track new transactions on Ethereum in real-time has been a game-changer for my dApp. This app gives me the data I need instantly.
TESTIMONIAL_2_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: I love how easy it is to integrate this app's API into my project. The filtering and querying options are incredibly powerful.
TESTIMONIAL_3_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: As someone building Ethereum infrastructure, having a reliable source of fresh transaction data is critical. This app delivers.
FEATURE_1_BODY: Stay up-to-date with the latest Ethereum transactions as they happen. Our app monitors the network and instantly notifies you of new activity.
FEATURE_2_BODY: Easily find specific transactions by filtering based on criteria like address, value, gas price, and more. Customize your search for precise results.
FEATURE_3_BODY: Get comprehensive details on each transaction, including the sender, recipient, value transferred, gas used, and input data decoded.
FEATURE_4_BODY: Seamlessly connect your Ethereum wallet to monitor transactions associated with your addresses and keep track of your balance.
FEATURE_5_BODY: Set up custom alerts to be notified when specific transaction conditions are met, such as large value transfers or interactions with smart contracts.
FEATURE_6_BODY: Export transaction data in various formats for further analysis, reporting, or integration with other tools and platforms.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Ethereum Transaction Finder
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app allows you to easily find and track new transactions on the Ethereum blockchain in real-time. Stay up-to-date on the latest activity.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We continuously monitor the Ethereum network and immediately detect when new transactions are broadcasted. Our app then notifies you of these new transactions.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: For each new transaction detected, we provide the transaction hash, from and to addresses, value transferred, gas used, and timestamp.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, we offer a 14-day free trial so you can test out our Ethereum transaction finder before subscribing to a paid plan.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about tracking new Ethereum transactions
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: This app allows you to monitor the Ethereum blockchain and receive alerts for new transactions as they occur. Stay up-to-date with the latest activity on the Ethereum network.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our app connects directly to Ethereum nodes, scanning the blockchain for new transaction data in real-time. When a new transaction is detected, you'll receive an instant notification.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What kind of transactions can I track?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: You can monitor all types of Ethereum transactions, including token transfers, smart contract deployments, and interactions with decentralized applications (dApps).
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, you can set up custom filters to only receive notifications for transactions that match specific criteria, such as transactions involving particular token contracts or wallet addresses.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We offer a free trial to test out the app's features. After the trial period, you'll need to subscribe to one of our paid plans to continue receiving transaction alerts.
